data.description: This could the home you're looking for in the lovely Country Meadows Subdivision. The home has a modern  yet cozy feel to it. It is incredibly well kept and the location is near great schools. This home features 4  spacious bedrooms and 3 full baths. The kitchen features granite counter tops throughout and overlooks the  dining area and living room. Master bedroom has great space and features a roomy shower plus a large  walk in closet. Great backyard with sprinkler system and a patio slab area great to BBQ or just to enjoy the  day. Call today to schedule your showing and make this house yours!
